title: 1x1 - COMING AT YOU THIS AUGUST 🍏🏫👩🏼‍🏫👩🏽‍🏫
posting_body: Tramor at Autumn Park is a welcoming, quiet apartment community conveniently located off of Highway 79 and close to IH-35.
We are just a moment's drive away from shops, dining, entertainment, and schools.
Enjoy a day of shopping at the Round Rock Premium Outlet Mall or swing by Dell Diamond to catch a game or two.
Students will have easy access to surrounding Round Rock ISD schools as well as multiple college campuses.
Texas State University, Texas A&M Health Science Center, and Austin Community College R.R. are all less than five miles from property.
We are pet friendly and would love to have you and your furry critters.
We have NO breed or weight restrictions.
Autumn Park is your one and only place for comfortable, easy living!
All we are missing is you!
*6 month lease terms have a $50.00 premium upcharge per month, 9 month lease terms have a $25.00 premium upcharge per month
This specific unit comes complete with the following:
Lots of storage space including a large built-in bookshelf
Plenty of natural lighting due to large windows and patio door
- Pet stations located throughout the property
- Pet friendly - no breed or weight restriction
- Poo Prints World DNA Pet Registry Program
Call, e-mail, or stop in for a tour of your new home today!
